{"tid":2117260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］小心呢間鋪賣假鞋［突發］","createTime":"2020-07-20T16:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T07:04:41.000Z","uid":204726,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"103a14ffb73bdb51bd3bed66d27022b792da856b","tid":2117260,"uid":204726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T16:57:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">借朋友ac！</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">篇文可能會1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋我都知自己衰戇尻 麻煩屌細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n事源我喺呢間IGshop買咗對鞋比朋友做生日禮物，我朋友收到對鞋之後發現對鞋重量輕過Nike flyknit跑鞋、同teva 涼鞋差唔多重量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係實物同照片對比係完全睇唔出有咩分別，可以話係極級高仿。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外觀睇係完全睇唔出有咩分別，但係色水嚟講膠味甚濃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZYj0gQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZYj0gQ.png&h=59ad843f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/happysneaker_hk?igshid=785v3vace4wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhappysneaker_hk%3Figshid%3D785v3vace4wk&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=2699b94b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/happysneaker_hk?igshid=785v3vace4wk</a><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">附上快捷link<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n於是我用sizes 唔適合為理由dm佢退貨，之後佢cap翻落單個段文字話標明咗任何尺碼理由不設退換。之後我就話，對鞋碼數實在唔適合我會放出去然後叫佢提供返收據俾我。第一次佢就用外國代購退稅嗰陣收左張單所以提供唔到為理由。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住第二個原因會睇到你企撚咗係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話唔suppose客人轉售所以幫唔到我。睇到呢句我激到癲撚咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ao1xAQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAo1xAQ0.png&h=87e70621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKxHX4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKxHX4m.jpg&h=eb9f1ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KBJHv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KBJHv1.jpg&h=6eedb248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwSwRpm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwSwRpm.png&h=b391266c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知今次係我戇鳩在先，但其實呢個款我朋友鍾意咗好耐⋯知道買咗對假鞋真係大家都好唔開心⋯所以一方面好嬲所以想呻下，一方面又好頹比人呃左信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺上呢度希望多啲人睇到呢間shop嘅所作所為，唔好有人好似我咁戇鳩⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後附上實物圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9806e5637e1df5ab306c21ee016707668e5d32","tid":2117260,"uid":70754,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"重點係點解無實體門市都照買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊呢個係最基本嘅條件"},{"pid":"3a66c4b6ccef13a78cd5de34c75e41bd34be8515","tid":2117260,"uid":70754,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"不嬲連交收都無，門市有無嘅，9成都係假<br />\n<br />\n依家好撚多呢啲快閃鬼shop，有對鞋收到算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間野早兩日我已經有留意，好似話疫情唔可以面交，笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e691cb5f4c4d61e670121ec9d52283501d5be88","tid":2117260,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"人類總係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cff643ade40365fb4599fff3aabf0d244bb504c","tid":2117260,"uid":204726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a66c4b6ccef13a78cd5de34c75e41bd34be8515","tid":2117260,"uid":70754,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"不嬲連交收都無，門市有無嘅，9成都係假<br />\n<br />\n依家好撚多呢啲快閃鬼shop，有對鞋收到算好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間野早兩日我已經有留意，好似話疫情唔可以面交，笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"下次會識醒目㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但其實好似有實鋪都唔一定係真？<br />\n有無咩tips提醒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631705b7f6240548fdbf2745e9bdb37d63e7317c","tid":2117260,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52b179f63733024fdae83017674ad2671d5a1264","tid":2117260,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"蠢閪<br />\n貪小便宜"},{"pid":"645293681be2dd0817066d7e965c01654a7d5493","tid":2117260,"uid":204726,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"52b179f63733024fdae83017674ad2671d5a1264","tid":2117260,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"蠢閪<br />\n貪小便宜"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"旺角波鞋街正價都係899喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e907552ca92cf5b24fb987d897aefa138876aff","tid":2117260,"uid":1188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite